stories.text:
I just got this Google Calendar invite from some unknown organizer, clearly affiliated with Boom:

Notification: Boom: A startup building a supersonic jet @ Thu Jun 30, 2022

Boom: A startup building a supersonic jet Thursday Jun 30, 2022 ⋅ 12am – 1:30am

Boom (from YC's W16 batch) is building a supersonic jet airliner. Blake Scholl, the founder, will take us a tour of the Boom aircraft factory and then he and YC President Geoff Ralston will talk about the early days of Boom and how he went from an idea to a plane. Location

https://ycombinator.zoom.us/j/<redacted> View map Organizer Unknown Organizer unknownorganizer@calendar.google.com

If you're a Boom employee, fuck your company and founder. I don't give a sh*t. Stop spamming me.
